parameters.query:
SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

select distinct b.ref_no,
to_char(b.created_at,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')as created_at, 
to_char(b.updated_at,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')as updated_at, 
to_char(b.request_start_at,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')as request_start_at, 
to_char(b.request_end_at,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')as request_end_at, 
l.user_id, 
concat(u2.first_name, ' ',u2.last_name)as guest_name,
concat(u.first_name, ' ',u.last_name)as host_name,
u.email, 
u.uuid, 
u.phone_number
from bookings b 
left join listings l on l.id = b.listing_id
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id 
left join users u2 on u2.id = b.user_id 
left join listing_location ll on ll.listing_id = b.listing_id 
where 1=1 
and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
and (b.status IN ('cancelled') AND b.reason !~* '(host|owner|avai|car)')
and b.updated_at between (NOW() - interval '10 minutes') and NOW()
--and l.registration_no = 'VKL7526'
order by 3 desc
--limit 1
